My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 19

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

The surviving teams face their first challenge as they race against the clock to prepare an eat on the go breakfast for Sydney's hungry commuters. The best dish as voted by the public will be safe from elimination and the weakest team, as chosen by the judges, will head straight to the first sudden death cook-off.
